title: An Unusual Bot Lane Pairing - Diamond Ranked Full Game Commentary
body:
Hey everyone,

I'm a Diamond support main, and I thought this'd be an interesting game to share because it's such an unusual pairing in the bot lane, Alistar and Vel'Koz.

A lot of people would say Vel'Koz as an APC is a troll pick - I wouldn't.

For clarification, this is a ranked game in Diamond.

If you're interested, check out the video above :)
